v8:item.v8:content:
A duplicate here is defined as a newly loaded fuel fill-up whose data matches the data of any fuel fill-up already in the database. Options for handling this situation:
Do not check - the duplicate will be loaded regardless, no messages are displayed;
Check - the duplicate will not be loaded, a message with brief information is displayed;
Warn - the duplicate will be loaded, a message with brief information is displayed.
